ox": [956.2, 870.6, 1006.6, 893.7]}, {"text": "17.4 %", "bbox": [1081.3, 870.6, 1142.1, 893.7]}, {"text": "2014 Versus 2013", "bbox": [93.8, 937.5, 249.5, 960.5]}, {"text": "Revenue generated by our Refrigeration & Food Equipment segment in 2014 increased $33.3 million, or 1.8%, compared to", "bbox": [93.8, 987.5, 1149.6, 1010.5]}, {"text": "2013. The overall increase in revenue includes organic growth of 1.7%, and acquisition growth of 0.2%. Foreign currency", "bbox": [93.8, 1012.5, 1149.6, 1035.6]}, {"text": "translation had an unfavorable impact of 0.1%.", "bbox": [93.8, 1037.5, 490.3, 1060.6]}, {"text": "•", "bbox": [131.3, 1087.5, 143.8, 1110.6]}, {"text": "Revenue growth in our Refrigeration end market (representing 77.2% of 2014 segment revenue) increased $33.3 million,", "bbox": [168.8, 1087.5, 1149.7, 1110.6]}, {"text": "or 2.3%, resulting from solid activity with major food retailers.", "bbox": [168.8, 1112.5, 699.6, 1135.6]}, {"text": "•", "bbox": [131.3, 1162.5, 143.8, 1185.6]}, {"text": "Revenue derived from Food Equipment (representing 22.8% of 2014 segment revenue) was flat year over year, where", "bbox": [168.8, 1162.5, 1149.7, 1185.6]}, {"text": "growth in commercial kitchen and can-forming equipments was offset by soft food processing equipment activity.", "bbox": [168.8, 1187.5, 1119.4, 1210.6]}, {"text": "Refrigeration & Food Equipment segment earnings in 2014 decreased $28.6 million, or 10.7%, compared with 2013, with a", "bbox": [93.8, 1237.6, 1149.6, 1260.6]}, {"text": "decrease in operating margin of 180 basis points. The earnings and margin decreases were driven by non-recurring restructuring", "bbox": [93.8, 1262.6, 1149.7, 1285.6]}, {"text": "of $24.9 million ($19.4 million higher as compared to 2013) primarily for the closure of a European-based facility, unfavorable", "bbox": [93.8, 1287.6, 1149.4, 1310.6]}, {"text": "product mix, as well as a $6.8 million land sale gain in the prior year that did not repeat.", "bbox": [93.8, 1312.6, 828.5, 1335.6]}, {"text": "Bookings for the year ended December 31, 2014 decreased slightly as compared to 2013, reflecting anticipated lower orders for", "bbox": [93.8, 1362.6, 1149.7, 1385.7]}, {"text": "Refrigeration and the timing of orders for Food Equipment. Backlog at December 31, 2014 decreased 18.6% due to the", "bbox": [93.8, 1387.6, 1149.6, 1410.7]}, {"text": "aforementioned timing of orders for Food Equipment. Book to bill was 0.97.", "bbox": [93.8, 1412.6, 732.9, 1435.7]}, {"text": "Table of Contents", "bbox": [85.5, 3.1, 233.4, 26.2]}]}